2011-07-08T10:07:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/powercom-co-ltd-june-sales-fall-49-81-table-3043-tt.html
POWERCOM CO LTD (3043)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 49.81% to NT$304,958,000 from NT$607,657,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            304,958          607,657    
YOY%             -49.81%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,459,425        2,384,931   
YOY%              3.12%  
=================================================================
 